1
00:01:28,570 --> 00:01:35,000
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty III:
To Chang'an]

2
00:01:35,550 --> 00:01:37,970
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:44,720
[Chengfo Temple]

4
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,400
[Guangxiao, Abbot of the Chengfo Temple]

5
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,000
Master!

6
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:57,770
Master!

7
00:01:59,229 --> 00:02:01,060
Why so panicked?

8
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,400
What is it?

9
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,510
Master,

10
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,870
I was just serving outside the door...

11
00:02:05,870 --> 00:02:06,710
Changqing,

12
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:09,000
you didn't hear anything.

13
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:09,130
But I really did hear it, Master.

14
00:02:09,130 --> 00:02:10,560
[Changqing, a disciple of Chengfo Temple]

15
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,000
It's that...

16
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,030
It's your unsettled heart

17
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:12,370
that leads to the noises you hear.

18
00:02:12,370 --> 00:02:14,000
[Chan]

19
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,410
Buddhism is boundless.

20
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:15,360
[Tranquility]

21
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,560
Adhering to Buddhism deep down inside,

22
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:18,250
we won't be disturbed

23
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:19,030
[Chan]

24
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,520
by outside noises.

25
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:21,840
You may leave now.

26
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:25,150
Even if it means defying my master,

27
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:26,770
I must speak my mind.

28
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,150
Ever since two months ago,

29
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:30,240
when people heard a woman crying
in the Great Buddha Hall,

30
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,079
the Chengfo Temple has completely changed.

31
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,079
Everyone in Chang'an is

32
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:34,480
saying that our temple is

33
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:36,000
haunted,

34
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,800
causing worshippers to dwindle.

35
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,740
Some timid monks

36
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,530
even left the temple directly.

37
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,910
What on earth are you trying to say?

38
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,680
Master,

39
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,190
how about we

40
00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:48,870
go find an exorcist?

41
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,960
Shut up!

42
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,840
You want the prestigious Chengfo Temple

43
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,240
to recruit an exorcist?

44
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,940
Isn't that the same as admitting

45
00:02:55,940 --> 00:02:57,870
that there are ghosts in our temple?

46
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,360
You're out of your mind!

47
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,620
Get out of my sight.

48
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,160
But, Master,

49
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,630
please listen.

50
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:06,830
Today, it's not just one,

51
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:09,430
but several women crying together,

52
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:10,120
Master.

53
00:03:11,370 --> 00:03:15,460
[Great Buddha Hall]

54
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:21,430
[Great Buddha Hall]

55
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:21,750
You,

56
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,430
go open the main gate.

57
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:24,430
Abbot, these...

58
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,870
These are clearly female ghosts wailing.

59
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,800
Are you trying to get us all killed?

60
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,240
I'm done with this job at Chengfo Temple.

61
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,260
I-I quit.

62
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:34,100
[Great Buddha Hall]

63
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,120
Fine.

64
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:38,180
If anyone wants to leave, just go!

65
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:39,950
Master,

66
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:41,520
why don't we come here tomorrow

67
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,380
during the day?

68
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,190
Shut up.

69
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,910
Now, everyone, follow me

70
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,910
and chant loudly.

71
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,380
Amitabha.

72
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:51,400
Amitabha.

73
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:52,430
Amitabha.

74
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,560
[Great Buddha Hall]

75
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,150
Amitabha.

76
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,750
Amitabha.

77
00:03:56,870 --> 00:03:57,750
Amitabha.

78
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,910
Amitabha.

79
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:04,240
Amitabha.

80
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,750
Amitabha.

81
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:11,030
Amitabha.

82
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,750
Amitabha.

83
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:17,680
Amitabha.

84
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:20,750
Amitabha.

85
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,160
Master,

86
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,160
the crying has stopped.

87
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,720
Indeed, the crying has stopped.

88
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,270
It's gone.

89
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,430
As expected,

90
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,610
these evil things

91
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,680
fear the righteous Buddhist power.

92
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,750
Amitabha.

93
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:42,770
Where is Householder Chenkong,

94
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,600
who guards the Great Buddha Hall?

95
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:47,130
He asked for leave at noon
to run some errands.

96
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:51,420
Someone must have used his absence

97
00:04:51,590 --> 00:04:53,590
to sneak into the Great Buddha Hall.

98
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,000
Light the sacred candles

99
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,070
and search everywhere.

100
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,120
Let me see

101
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,380
who was so bold

102
00:04:58,510 --> 00:04:59,870
as to fake women's cries

103
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,360
in the Great Buddha Hall to scare people.

104
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:02,830
Search!

105
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:08,600
Abbot,

106
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,070
we didn't find anything.

107
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,040
Beneath this Great Buddha,

108
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,430
there used to be a secret passage
to the Ghost Market.

109
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:13,360
Could the crying

110
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:15,160
be coming from there?

111
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,120
Impossible.

112
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,310
After Feng Han's rebellion,

113
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,510
the government ordered people

114
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,630
to seal that secret passage

115
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:22,830
with huge rocks.

116
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:25,560
Even if there had been
crying in the Ghost Market,

117
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,240
it wouldn't have reached here.

118
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:27,830
Look,

119
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:30,390
the demons and monsters on this wall are

120
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:32,190
thoroughly covered by cobwebs.

121
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,830
The power of Buddha is infinite.

122
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,270
From now on, if you hear

123
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:36,120
any sounds,

124
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:38,000
don't be afraid anymore.

125
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,720
Remember my words.

126
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:43,950
When a monk's mind is at peace,

127
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,490
he won't hear any sounds that disturb him.

128
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:51,830
Amitabha.

129
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:55,159
Amitabha.

130
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,000
It's happening again, Master!

131
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,240
There's no one in the hall.

132
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,240
It must be the Three Witches crying!

133
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,120
Don't panic.

134
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:24,240
Don't run! Come back!

135
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,540
Come back here!

136
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:27,830
Master!

137
00:06:30,130 --> 00:06:34,190
[The Crying Sound from Chengfo Temple]

138
00:06:40,310 --> 00:06:40,340
There are four joys today.

139
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,720
[Great virtue can carry the world]

140
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,159
So I've prepared four dishes

141
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,190
for you to enjoy.

142
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,240
Don't dive in so fast.

143
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:50,800
Xijun,

144
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:52,710
what are these four joys?

145
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,190
Please tell us.

146
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,600
The first joy is

147
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,190
Master Ji's recovery, of course.

148
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:05,480
That's thanks to you guys
taking good care of me.

149
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:07,000
The second joy is

150
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,830
that you, Lu Lingfeng, have been

151
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:11,160
promoted to Yongzhou Judicial Official.

152
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,310
The third joy is

153
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:16,070
that, according to His Majesty's decree,

154
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:20,040
my sworn brother's been confirmed
as the Criminal Investigation Scholar.

155
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,970
The fourth joy is

156
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,430
the greatest of all.

157
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,190
It is

158
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:27,430
that Xue Huan has become a captain.

159
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:28,040
I believe

160
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,250
he must be the Tang Empire's

161
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,600
youngest captain ever.

162
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,390
Thank you for your guidance, Master.

163
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,800
These first three joys,

164
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:39,320
compared to Xue Huan's joy, are

165
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,040
nothing at all.

166
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,220
Especially you two,

167
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:45,800
who used to serve as Vice Minister
of the Judicial Review Court.

168
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:48,000
But now, you hold such minor positions.

169
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,680
Fei,

170
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,120
you're wrong.

171
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:55,390
No matter how high-ranking an official is
in the Tang Empire,

172
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:57,270
we all serve His Majesty

173
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:59,190
and work for the people's welfare.

174
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:00,920
What's wrong with a minor position?

175
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,120
Does the duty change?

176
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,770
These are indeed four joys

177
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,240
worthy of proper celebration.

178
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:07,390
[Great virtue can carry the world]

179
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:09,250
Let me use Xijun's wine to propose

180
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,560
a toast to everyone.

181
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:12,360
Come on.

182
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,250
Let's drink.

183
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,000
Fei.

184
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:26,160
Why do you keep stopping me?

185
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:27,970
Xijun has put in so much effort

186
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,170
to prepare such exquisite dishes.

187
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,070
Wouldn't it be a waste

188
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,580
to eat them right away?

189
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,000
Just looking with your eyes

190
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,530
without eating
won't satisfy your appetite!

191
00:08:38,549 --> 00:08:39,350
In my opinion,

192
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:42,030
we should build on the original dish names

193
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:44,150
and give each dish a new name,

194
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,650
which must be poetic and artistic

195
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,960
to match this beautiful occasion.

196
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,960
Lu Lingfeng,

197
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:52,840
when did you also become

198
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,150
so sentimental?

199
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,120
I actually like

200
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:03,280
Lu Lingfeng's idea.

201
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,960
Now we've returned to Chang'an.

202
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,160
Life should be filled with more poetry.

203
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:08,720
Let me go first.

204
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,470
This honey-sesame fried pastry

205
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,440
[Dish: Victory Over Foreigners]

206
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:17,040
is originally named
Victory Over Foreigners.

207
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:19,480
Now, I'll name it

208
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:24,480
Fallen Flowers Scattered Like Stars.

209
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,530
Brilliant!

210
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:29,000
These pastries look like flowers.

211
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,970
The sesame seeds on it resemble
clusters of stars.

212
00:09:31,970 --> 00:09:33,080
[Dish: Victory Over Foreigners]

213
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,080
Fallen flowers on the ground

214
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:35,620
are just like the stars in the sky.

215
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:37,830
[Dish:
Fallen Flowers Scattered Like Stars]

216
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,500
Brilliant!

217
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,650
Xue Huan.

218
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,390
As for this shrimp,

219
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,080
let me think.

220
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:52,630
Though this shrimp is grilled,

221
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:54,230
it is transparent throughout.

222
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:55,120
[Dish: Bright Grilled Shrimp]

223
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:58,000
It's originally called
Bright Grilled Shrimp.

224
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,900
I've got it!

225
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,320
I'll call it

226
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:04,300
Cold Beacon Fire on Radiant Armor.

227
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:05,910
[Dish: Bright Grilled Shrimp]

228
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,360
The Radiant Armor

229
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:08,520
is worn by warriors of the Tang Empire.

230
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,880
[Dish: Cold Beacon Fire on Radiant Armor]

231
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,850
The beacon fire being cold on the armor

232
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,840
captures both the poetic sentiment
of the frontier

233
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,750
and the imagery in one's mind.

234
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:18,910
Great!

235
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:20,790
I can see

236
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,510
a hint of artistic talent

237
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:24,320
between your brows now.

238
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,460
There are two more dishes.

239
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,360
Let me try.

240
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:35,810
This dish in front of me

241
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:39,600
shall be called Auspicious Dragon
and Phoenix in Crystal Delight.

242
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,720
Well done!

243
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:42,120
This dish was originally called

244
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,980
Crystal Dragon and Phoenix Cake.

245
00:10:44,050 --> 00:10:44,120
[Dish: Crystal Dragon and Phoenix Cake]

246
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,750
You put dragon and phoenix in front

247
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,810
and crystal after.

248
00:10:47,030 --> 00:10:47,680
It immediately creates

249
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,390
[Dish: Auspicious Dragon
and Phoenix in Crystal Delight]

250
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:50,050
a vivid picture in one's mind.

251
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,390
For the last dish,

252
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,110
I'll do it.

253
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,530
This scallion and vinegar chicken

254
00:10:57,790 --> 00:11:00,270
is my lifelong favorite.

255
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:02,670
I'll give it a new name.

256
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,890
Let's call it...

257
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,770
Pure Tangy Fragrance
that Intoxicates the Heart.

258
00:11:06,770 --> 00:11:09,920
[Dish: Scallion and Vinegar Chicken]

259
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:10,910
[Dish: Pure Tangy Fragrance
that Intoxicates the Heart]

260
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:11,910
What do you think?

261
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,080
What do you think?

262
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,670
What do you think?

263
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:22,800
Xue Huan,

264
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,940
what do you say?

265
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:32,910
I-I think it's quite good.

266
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,360
So, all this time,

267
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,910
you two pairs

268
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:40,720
have been teaming up to tease me,

269
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,450
haven't you?

270
00:11:41,910 --> 00:11:42,630
Penalty drink!

271
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:42,740
Penalty drink!

272
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:44,440
[Great virtue can carry the world]

273
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:44,790
Come.

274
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,120
-Come.
-Come.

275
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,850
Come, accept your punishment.

276
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:48,890
-Come.
-Drink!

277
00:11:52,530 --> 00:11:53,550
Lu Lingfeng,

278
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:55,710
what I'm most concerned about now

279
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,870
is my so-called position

280
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:00,180
as Criminal Investigation Scholar.

281
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:02,790
It's not a
regular court official position.

282
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,390
Du Ming is refusing
to pay my monthly salary again.

283
00:12:06,390 --> 00:12:08,120
Food is expensive in Chang'an.

284
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,320
What am I to do?

285
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,600
You have

286
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,550
that special fund

287
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:23,200
allocated for secret agents.

288
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:25,120
It must be substantial, right?

289
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:28,790
Though my scholar rank isn't high,

290
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:29,960
it was

291
00:12:30,790 --> 00:12:32,320
appointed by the Princess.

292
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,000
His Majesty also approved it.

293
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,000
At the very least,

294
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:37,960
I should be treated
as a seventh-rank official, right?

295
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,320
That job of yours

296
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,240
as Yongzhou Prefecture's
Chief of Secret Agents...

297
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,500
I've done the work too.

298
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:45,850
You should give me
two monthly salaries, shouldn't you?

299
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:49,910
Dream on.

300
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:54,530
One salary is fine too,

301
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,790
but the amount can't be too small.

302
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:57,700
Tell me,

303
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:59,350
how much can you give?

304
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,240
One month...

305
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,700
How about 1,500 coins?

306
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,240
That little?

307
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:07,810
Take it or leave it.

308
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,200
Let's negotiate a bit more.

309
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,240
Can you add a little more?

310
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:14,000
I have a whole family

311
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,660
to support.

312
00:13:16,790 --> 00:13:18,320
Which member of this family

313
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,100
actually needs your support?

314
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:20,630
I...

315
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:22,810
Xijun has always been wealthy

316
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:25,650
and she has exceptional painting skills.

317
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,320
Xue Huan is now

318
00:13:27,390 --> 00:13:29,320
a captain of Yongzhou Prefecture.

319
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,680
He has his own salary.

320
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:31,840
As for Fei,

321
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,520
I'll take care of him

322
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:35,080
for life.

323
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:37,000
You and I live in official quarters

324
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,600
and don't need to buy houses.

325
00:13:38,630 --> 00:13:40,030
What do you need money for?

326
00:13:40,030 --> 00:13:41,550
But I have Yingtao!

327
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:43,240
Yingtao is alert

328
00:13:43,350 --> 00:13:44,670
and has excellent martial skills,

329
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:46,130
as well as street tactics.

330
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,550
She's perfect as a secret agent.

331
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,120
I'm planning to hire her.

332
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:52,930
That's good.

333
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:53,970
That's good.

334
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:56,730
Then I'll help negotiate her salary.

335
00:13:57,510 --> 00:13:58,390
Her monthly salary

336
00:13:58,390 --> 00:13:59,870
can be less than mine

337
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,510
but not by too much.

338
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:02,800
Two thousand coins.

339
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,330
What's wrong?

340
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:05,960
Yingtao is worth this price.

341
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:07,560
The missions she'll be doing

342
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:09,080
are all very dangerous.

343
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:10,750
For me...

344
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,800
she's much more useful than you.

345
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,880
Thank you, Official Lu.

346
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,750
From now on, I, Yingtao,

347
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,000
will no longer be idle in Chang'an.

348
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,060
I'll have work to do

349
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:25,470
and a monthly salary.

350
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,060
W-Well,

351
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:29,200
she shouldn't earn more than me!

352
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:30,490
That's not fair.

353
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:32,230
Enough. Stop being so petty.

354
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,570
If worst comes to worst,

355
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:35,080
I'll support you.

356
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:45,910
[Yongzhou Prefecture]

357
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:47,080
I haven't even started working yet

358
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,240
and already got paid.

359
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,260
I'm free today too.

360
00:14:49,260 --> 00:14:49,870
Xijun,

361
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,930
let's go eat something delicious.

362
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:53,440
Yingtao,

363
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,030
I was actually planning to invite you

364
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:56,200
to go with me to...

365
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,570
The cosmetics shop?

366
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,480
Yes!

367
00:14:59,270 --> 00:15:00,220
Look at that.

368
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,200
I was also thinking

369
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,390
about going to the cosmetics shop,

370
00:15:02,390 --> 00:15:04,000
but I was afraid you'd think I'm shallow.

371
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,670
Everyone has a love for beauty.

372
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:06,440
There's nothing shallow about that.

373
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:09,160
Great minds think alike then.

374
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:09,850
Let's go.

375
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,490
Let's go.

376
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,600
Official Lu, busy?

377
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,510
Come on.

378
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,500
Have some tea and take a break.

379
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,380
Come, come,

380
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,630
take a rest.

381
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:30,720
For Yingtao,

382
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,090
you've really gone to great lengths.

383
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,770
This Chang'an

384
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,460
is a city

385
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:38,610
and also a world of its own.

386
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,410
However, it's too vast.

387
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:44,430
So vast that it makes outsiders

388
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:46,320
feel empty inside.

389
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:48,430
In the world of Chang'an,

390
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,300
Yingtao has no family or friends.

391
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:53,120
So, I want her to quickly develop

392
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:54,750
a sense of belonging.

393
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:57,700
Thankfully, your cooperation

394
00:15:57,750 --> 00:15:59,210
was absolutely flawless.

395
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,150
Thank you for your help.

396
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:01,750
Thank you.

397
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,000
The journey to the west
was full of dangers.

398
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,030
Madam Yingtao

399
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:09,450
joined forces with me many times
to eliminate villains.

400
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,360
I'm not just helping

401
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,670
you, Su Wuming.

402
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:13,570
No need for thanks.

403
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:14,520
Hey...

404
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:22,000
I've served as the Judicial Official

405
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,000
of Yongzhou Prefecture before

406
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,000
but only briefly.

407
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:25,770
This time,

408
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,440
I want to remain

409
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,880
in this position longer.

410
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,610
I'm planning to implement
some new measures.

411
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:32,650
Want to hear it?

412
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,490
Go ahead.

413
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:35,770
[Map of Chang'an]

414
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,140
The Tang Empire's capital of Chang'an

415
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:37,910
[Map of Chang'an]

416
00:16:37,910 --> 00:16:39,640
originally had 108 districts.

417
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:41,870
During Emperor Gaozong's reign,
Daming Palace was built,

418
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:42,250
splitting Yongchang and Yishan
into two separate districts,

419
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:44,390
[Map of Chang'an]

420
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:45,790
making it 110 districts.

421
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:48,070
The capital is complex, like a maze.

422
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:50,610
Governing it is extremely difficult.

423
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,730
There are some remote areas

424
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:55,520
that government offices can hardly reach.

425
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,660
So, I'm thinking of

426
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:58,910
moving the Judicial Official's court

427
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:00,020
to each district.

428
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,840
Each day, we'll go into one district,

429
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,870
handling new cases and resolving old ones.

430
00:17:03,870 --> 00:17:04,869
What do you think?

431
00:17:06,210 --> 00:17:07,000
[Map of Chang'an]

432
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,640
Circuit Trials around the City

433
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,790
with mobile offices

434
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,109
is unprecedented!

435
00:17:13,030 --> 00:17:14,829
But your new initiative

436
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:16,440
requires manpower.

437
00:17:16,589 --> 00:17:17,200
How about this?

438
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:17,920
I suggest

439
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:19,910
transferring Jia, Luo, and Liu

440
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,349
from Chang'an County.

441
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,920
That's exactly what I was thinking.

442
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:28,200
Are we that in sync now?

443
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:31,310
[Shengye District]

444
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,310
Miss, take a look.

445
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:33,400
Five coins each.

446
00:17:34,850 --> 00:17:41,270
[Meixiu Skincare Shop]

447
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:42,490
I've been here several times already.

448
00:17:42,490 --> 00:17:43,110
[Rouge]

449
00:17:43,110 --> 00:17:44,720
Why is it always out of stock?

450
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,590
Exactly!

451
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,310
Everyone says
your Fairy Beauty Powder is good,

452
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:48,330
but what's the point if we can't buy it?

453
00:17:48,330 --> 00:17:50,070
[Huadian]

454
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,160
Just tell us how many days
until it's available.

455
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:54,000
How much longer? Tell us!

456
00:17:54,030 --> 00:17:55,160
Hurry up and tell us!

457
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:57,280
It'll be... three more days.

458
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,880
Please come early in three days.

459
00:17:58,880 --> 00:17:59,550
It'll be available.

460
00:17:59,550 --> 00:18:00,440
Three days?

461
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:02,070
Is it because too many people
are buying it

462
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:03,550
and the production can't keep up?

463
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:04,310
How about

464
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:05,880
you sell us the recipe

465
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:06,640
for your Celestial Beauty Powder?

466
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:07,590
We can make it ourselves.

467
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,340
-Yeah.
-No.

468
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,790
If you can't make enough yourself,

469
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:10,750
you might as well sell the recipe.

470
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:11,080
No...

471
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,660
Who wants to buy my recipe?

472
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:19,050
You want to buy the recipe?

473
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,640
Go and buy

474
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,590
all the shops

475
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,200
in Shengye District

476
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,130
to trade with me.

477
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:26,240
I'll accept the deal immediately!

478
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:26,960
Chi Ying,

479
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,900
we weren't being serious.

480
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:29,140
If there's no stock,
then there's no stock.

481
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:30,270
[Beauty Store Owner, Chi Ying]

482
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:31,640
Come back in three days.

483
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:32,680
Alright.

484
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:33,880
We'll be going now.

485
00:18:34,070 --> 00:18:34,750
Goodbye.

486
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:37,280
Wu Yang.

487
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:43,410
What did I tell you?

488
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:45,640
Whenever someone asks for our recipe,

489
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,350
put on a stern face and throw them out.

490
00:18:47,350 --> 00:18:47,720
[Chi Ying's daughter, Wu Yang]

491
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,590
Yes, Mother.

492
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,460
Have you practiced

493
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:51,790
that stern face I taught you?

494
00:18:51,790 --> 00:18:52,850
I still can't do it.

495
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:55,620
Silly girl.

496
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:57,690
Watch again.

497
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:08,750
Copy me

498
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:09,880
and show me.

499
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,230
Get out!

500
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,000
Getâ€”

501
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:20,270
Mother.

502
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,310
I just got here.

503
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,550
Mr. Yu.

504
00:19:26,350 --> 00:19:27,570
I just paid the rent.

505
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:29,480
You're not raising the rent again,
are you?

506
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,010
Chi Ying,

507
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:30,240
I came today

508
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:30,790
[Landlord Yu Gong]

509
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:32,720
to pick out a hairpiece for my wife.

510
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,680
I'm not collecting or raising

511
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,400
the rent.

512
00:19:36,270 --> 00:19:37,670
Then go ahead and choose.

513
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:39,250
I'll give you a good price.

514
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:43,160
How's business lately?

515
00:19:43,270 --> 00:19:43,930
Just so-so.

516
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,970
If you raise the rent again,

517
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:48,830
I'll be losing money.

518
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,720
Actually, the rent increase the other day

519
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,070
was just following market trends.

520
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:53,400
The property values in Shengye District

521
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,400
keep going up.

522
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:55,170
However,

523
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:56,310
my wife gave me

524
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,580
quite a scolding.

525
00:19:57,790 --> 00:20:00,000
She said Meixiu Skincare Shop
is doing well.

526
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:00,830
The Fairy Beauty Powder

527
00:20:00,830 --> 00:20:02,030
is especially famous.

528
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,370
You renting my shop

529
00:20:03,550 --> 00:20:04,610
is my good fortune.

530
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,960
She also said if I raise the rent

531
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,070
and upset you,

532
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,000
causing you to move out,

533
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,200
she won't forgive me.

534
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:10,200
So...

535
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:13,040
What's this?

536
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:15,110
I'm returning the extra rent to you.

537
00:20:20,350 --> 00:20:22,550
You're actually returning rent money?

538
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:23,750
Mr. Yu,

539
00:20:24,380 --> 00:20:25,350
you don't have some ulterior motive,

540
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:26,240
do you?

541
00:20:27,470 --> 00:20:28,470
Chi Ying,

542
00:20:28,720 --> 00:20:29,750
I came here in good faith
to return the money,

543
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:31,350
yet you're suspicious of me.

544
00:20:31,590 --> 00:20:33,720
If you don't want it, I'll take it back.

545
00:20:34,090 --> 00:20:35,920
Your rent increase
wasn't fair to begin with.

546
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:37,120
You should return it.

547
00:20:37,180 --> 00:20:39,040
I don't need to owe you any favors.

548
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:39,830
Pick one

549
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,130
and it's on the house.

550
00:20:41,130 --> 00:20:42,240
I haven't decided yet.

551
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,230
I don't need the hairpiece for free.

552
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:44,560
I'll pay the full price.

553
00:20:48,110 --> 00:20:48,640
Chi Ying,

554
00:20:49,590 --> 00:20:51,030
in these peaceful and prosperous times,

555
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:52,550
with music and dance flourishing,

556
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:53,550
both men and women

557
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:55,720
need to maintain their appearance.

558
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,550
Have you thought about opening

559
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:58,350
more shops in Chang'an?

560
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:58,920
No.

561
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,130
This is the only one.

562
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,680
You don't need to worry about capital.

563
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,880
I can be your partner.

564
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:06,720
I, Chi Ying,

565
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:08,610
never go into business

566
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:10,400
with others.

567
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,330
We have customers.

568
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:29,720
Ladies,

569
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:30,960
what would you like to buy?

570
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,680
We have face powder, eyebrow ink,

571
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:33,830
lip rouge, nail polish,

572
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,720
and huadian decorations of all shapes.

573
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,240
We've heard about

574
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:38,680
the Fairy Beauty Powder.

575
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:40,280
We came specifically for it.

576
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,140
The last batch is sold out.

577
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:44,570
New stock will be available in three days.

578
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:46,680
I've heard that the Fairy Beauty Powder

579
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,590
can remove spots and blemishes,

580
00:21:47,590 --> 00:21:48,920
and enhance skin radiance.

581
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,000
Is it really that miraculous?

582
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:50,720
Yes, it is.

583
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,830
Could you

584
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:53,920
teach me how to make the Beauty Powder?

585
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:55,720
I'd like to try it myself at home.

586
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,810
You two, get out!

587
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:07,860
Please!

588
00:22:12,550 --> 00:22:13,200
Chi Ying,

589
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:14,310
about what I mentioned last time,

590
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:15,710
have you made a decision?

591
00:22:15,790 --> 00:22:16,520
Zhang Kuang!

592
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:16,820
I've already told you

593
00:22:16,820 --> 00:22:17,680
[Owner of Zhang's Fish Shop, Zhang Kuang]

594
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:18,830
I won't sell my recipe.

595
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:20,160
What are you trying to do,

596
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,890
bringing these men here today?

597
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:28,160
This is Chang'an.

598
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,720
Don't tell me you're planning to rob me.

599
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:32,470
I know this is Chang'an,

600
00:22:32,830 --> 00:22:34,290
where laws are respected.

601
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,880
That's why I had to come in person.

602
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:37,880
-Yes, yes, yes.
-Yes, yes, yes.

603
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,210
Recently, I bought a box

604
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:41,200
of the Fairy Beauty Powder from your shop.

605
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:41,920
I went home

606
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,450
and gave it to my wife to use.

607
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,480
We thought it would make her beautiful,

608
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,480
but after applying it,

609
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:47,140
her face broke out in pimples!

610
00:22:47,330 --> 00:22:47,940
Tell me.

611
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,680
How will you compensate me?

612
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:50,480
You're lying.

613
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,590
Bring your wife to my shop,

614
00:22:52,590 --> 00:22:53,850
so I can see for myself.

615
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,310
How cruel of you!

616
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:57,530
How can a woman

617
00:22:57,830 --> 00:22:59,290
with a face full of pimples

618
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:01,030
casually go out in public?

619
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,300
How about this?

620
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,160
You two,

621
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:06,110
quickly write down

622
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:07,440
the recipe for the Fairy Powder

623
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,920
and I'll find someone to fix this myself.

624
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:09,880
In your dreams!

625
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:11,330
In my dreams.

626
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:13,030
Then I'll pay.

627
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:14,410
I'll give you...

628
00:23:16,310 --> 00:23:17,350
50,000 coins.

629
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,570
I'll buy everything in your shop,

630
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,510
including,

631
00:23:20,830 --> 00:23:22,440
of course, the recipe
for the Fairy Powder.

632
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,520
But my condition is

633
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:25,680
for you and your daughter
to take the money and leave.

634
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,810
Get out of Chang'an.

635
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:29,160
Fifty thousand coins?

636
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,860
Master, you're too merciful.

637
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,750
Yeah. You even refuse to earn the money.

638
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:35,030
As the shopkeeper,
why are you still hesitating?

639
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:35,760
Zhang Kuang!

640
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,070
As long as I, Chi Ying, am alive,

641
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:38,160
you won't succeed.

642
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:44,330
Aren't you just trying to
force her to sell the goods?

643
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,060
And who are you?

644
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:51,100
I'm someone who doesn't like you.

645
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:55,550
This is interesting.

646
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:58,310
Hit her.

647
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,380
-Yes!
-Yes!

648
00:24:00,370 --> 00:24:02,940
[Meixiu Skincare Shop]

649
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,310
Master!

650
00:24:13,550 --> 00:24:14,270
Chi Ying.

651
00:24:15,030 --> 00:24:17,030
So you've hired someone
to guard your shop?

652
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:17,870
That's right.

653
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,330
I'm the one she hired to guard the shop.

654
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,020
-Master!
-Master!

655
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:29,200
It hurts!

656
00:24:29,270 --> 00:24:30,200
This is not okay!

657
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:31,200
It's going to break!

658
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:31,920
Be gentle!

659
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:32,450
It's going to break!

660
00:24:32,450 --> 00:24:34,550
In the capital of the Tang Empire
under the Five Mausoleums,

661
00:24:34,550 --> 00:24:36,750
everyone is supposed to be kind
with great integrity.

662
00:24:36,750 --> 00:24:38,440
How come there are people like you?

663
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:40,070
You're trying to blackmail them
because their business is good.

664
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:40,950
What kind of logic is that?

665
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:42,880
Aren't I just want the Fairy Powder

666
00:24:42,890 --> 00:24:44,360
to be sold to more women?

667
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,770
I have good intentions.

668
00:24:46,590 --> 00:24:47,510
You're talking nonsense!

669
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:49,420
You're just trying to blackmail us!

670
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:50,750
If you don't want your arms to be broken,

671
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:51,950
just get lost at once!

672
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:52,590
Get lost now!

673
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:53,310
I'm leaving!

674
00:24:53,310 --> 00:24:54,240
I'm leaving now!

675
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:56,310
Master.

676
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:00,570
Loser!

677
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:01,870
Yes, yes, yes.

678
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:05,190
As a woman who can brawl,

679
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,130
do you dare to tell me your name?

680
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,440
Where do you live?

681
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:10,320
It's better not to tell you.

682
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:12,480
I'm doing this for your own good.

683
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:13,890
Otherwise,

684
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:14,960
you'll meet someone

685
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,490
whose temper is even worse.

686
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:19,050
Then your arms and legs might get broken,

687
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:20,440
and it'll be great pain.

688
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:21,110
Fine.

689
00:25:22,110 --> 00:25:24,270
I'll be able to find you guys
sooner or later.

690
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:24,960
Just wait.

691
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:29,320
Let's go.

692
00:25:32,510 --> 00:25:33,040
Let's go!

693
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:34,390
Let's go!

694
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:37,240
Get out of my way!

695
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:38,730
Step aside!

696
00:25:38,750 --> 00:25:40,810
-Thank you.
-What are you looking at?

697
00:25:41,270 --> 00:25:42,160
Let's go!

698
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:44,200
Thank you both for your help.

699
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,220
Let's talk inside.

700
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:46,700
No need.

701
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,000
We're here to buy

702
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,400
the Fairy Beauty Powder.

703
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,720
Since you've mentioned it's out of stock,

704
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:52,450
then we'll come again in 3 days.

705
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:53,550
Take care, Ma'am.

706
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:56,110
If those thugs come again
to cause trouble,

707
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,310
you can go to the Yongzhou Prefecture

708
00:25:57,310 --> 00:25:58,920
to find Lu Lingfeng,
the Judicial Official.

709
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,310
He will definitely help you.

710
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:00,840
Let's go.

711
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:04,010
Ladies, my saviors!

712
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:05,920
Wu Yang.

713
00:26:06,200 --> 00:26:07,260
The Beauty Powder!

714
00:26:08,270 --> 00:26:09,400
The Fairy Beauty Powder

715
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:10,880
is indeed out of stock at the counter.

716
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:12,590
But I still have some for my personal use.

717
00:26:12,590 --> 00:26:14,170
If you two don't mind...

718
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,270
Ladies,

719
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,440
these are gifts for you.

720
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,240
You don't need to pay.

721
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:17,830
Wu Yang.

722
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:21,100
You should have
let me say the last sentence.

723
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:22,720
Yes.

724
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,640
They're gifts for you two.
You don't need to pay.

725
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:27,570
This is not okay.

726
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:29,490
Let me pay.

727
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,110
I've heard it costs 100 monedas per box.

728
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:33,310
Here are 200 monedas.

729
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:36,590
Bye.

730
00:26:37,350 --> 00:26:38,510
Thanks. Thanks.

731
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,720
It smells so good!

732
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:45,920
Please wait, ladies!

733
00:26:48,790 --> 00:26:50,650
I really can't accept this money.

734
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:53,630
What's your name?

735
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:54,550
Wu Yang.

736
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:55,870
W-u, Wu.

737
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:56,860
Y-a-n-g, Yang.

738
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,740
What a beautiful name.

739
00:26:59,070 --> 00:26:59,960
But you must

740
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,220
accept this money.

741
00:27:01,270 --> 00:27:01,830
Yeah.

742
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:02,660
Otherwise,

743
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,480
how could we

744
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:05,340
buy stuff at your store next time?

745
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:06,170
Let's go.

746
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:10,880
Wait!

747
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,280
What's wrong?

748
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:16,000
Can I be friends with you two?

749
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:18,400
I don't have any friends.

750
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:24,730
-Of course.
-Of course.

751
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:27,480
Wu Yang.

752
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:29,750
The comb on your bun is so beautiful.

753
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:37,240
Wu Yang.

754
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:38,990
May I ask you a question?

755
00:27:39,110 --> 00:27:40,200
Where's your father?

756
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,440
I've never met my father.

757
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:43,030
I've been with my mother
since I was a kid.

758
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:44,790
Is your mother

759
00:27:44,790 --> 00:27:46,450
usually very strict with you?

760
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,590
My mother treats me very well.

761
00:27:48,830 --> 00:27:49,440
Oh, by the way,

762
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,720
if you're free tomorrow,

763
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:51,920
shall we go to the Qu River to have fun?

764
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:52,720
Sure.

765
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:54,330
I've never been to the Qu River before.

766
00:27:54,330 --> 00:27:55,480
It's settled then.

767
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:57,260
At 9 AM,

768
00:27:57,510 --> 00:27:59,000
let's meet at the entrance
of the Chengfo Temple.

769
00:27:59,000 --> 00:27:59,400
Okay.

770
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:01,600
See you tomorrow then.

771
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:05,880
In Chang'an,

772
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,000
I, Chu Yingtao,

773
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:09,000
am finally making new friends, too.

774
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:10,600
Let's go.

775
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:18,480
With the clear Yi River,
Empress Wu Zetian was born.

776
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:21,720
With the murky Luo River,
Empress Wu Zetian ascended to Heaven.

777
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:24,270
Yet today,
we're witnessing Qu River's flood tide.

778
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:27,400
Empress Wu Zetian will be reborn
to sit in the imperial court.

779
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,480
I am Empress Wu Zetian.

780
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:29,330
I will sit in the imperial court.

781
00:28:29,330 --> 00:28:29,640
[Night Watch]

782
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:30,700
Then I am Master Di.

783
00:28:30,750 --> 00:28:32,150
I'll be your good friend.

784
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:33,160
What nonsense are you talking about?

785
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,160
Do you want to die?

786
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:37,070
Be careful, or I'll summon ghosts

787
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,320
to devour you two!

788
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,200
Di Renjie!

789
00:28:41,350 --> 00:28:43,350
Wait for me! Just wait for me!

790
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:49,480
It's scorching in summer!

791
00:28:52,030 --> 00:28:54,110
Beware of fire!

792
00:28:54,550 --> 00:28:56,480
Guard against theft and robbery!

793
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:02,680
It's scorching in summer!

794
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,750
Stay calm and patient!

795
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:08,550
-Guard against theft and robbery!
-Stop right there!

796
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:13,400
I'm quite impatient now.

797
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:20,730
Your face...

798
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:22,890
Why is it painted so strangely?

799
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:25,200
Does that have anything to do with you?

800
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,350
You...

801
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,630
You're actually beautiful.

802
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,880
And you have such a graceful figure.

803
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:36,590
Why are you doing such a hard job?

804
00:29:37,110 --> 00:29:37,790
[Street Hooligan, Kuai Wu]

805
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:38,520
How about...

806
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,110
coming to my home
to do the night watch work?

807
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:42,750
Hundreds of ghosts are roaming at night.

808
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:44,410
Bystanders should stay away!

809
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,790
Who are you trying to scare?

810
00:29:46,850 --> 00:29:47,510
Let go of me!

811
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:48,510
Let go of me!

812
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,720
You villain!

813
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:51,890
I'll curse you!

814
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:53,000
Within the distance of 7 zhang,

815
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:55,270
there will be evil ghosts
trying to kill you!

816
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:57,000
Within the distance of 7 zhang,

817
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:58,460
there will be evil ghosts?

818
00:29:58,590 --> 00:29:59,440
Where are they?

819
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,300
Where are they?

820
00:30:05,110 --> 00:30:05,770
Are they...

821
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,110
in that well?

822
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:08,750
Ghosts!

823
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:09,920
Old ghosts!

824
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,350
Old ghosts!

825
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:12,720
Come out!

826
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:21,960
Empress Wu Zetian!

827
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:22,680
Empress Wu Zetian!

828
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:24,030
Ma'am, please don't be angry.

829
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:25,350
Those love affairs about you,
which I mentioned,

830
00:30:25,350 --> 00:30:26,610
were all nonsense!

831
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:28,110
They were all nonsense!

832
00:30:28,110 --> 00:30:29,240
I also didn't make them up myself.

833
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,840
I heard them all from others.

834
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,680
I'm drunk.

835
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:41,350
It was just a hallucination.

836
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,480
She's gone now, isn't she?

837
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,550
You nasty hag!

838
00:31:06,070 --> 00:31:07,750
