new judicial measures.

844
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:41,020
That's indeed what my son is like.

845
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:42,370
He's so enterprising.

846
00:31:42,590 --> 00:31:45,590
This measure has been approved
by the Yongzhou Prefecture.

847
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:48,720
It is said that they'll
start visiting districts today.

848
00:31:49,110 --> 00:31:50,750
Which district will they visit first?

849
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:52,750
It seems to be the Shengye District.

850
00:32:03,590 --> 00:32:05,190
As you previously reported,

851
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:06,510
in the districts of Chang'an,

852
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:08,970
what ballad is being sung
and spread around?

853
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:09,580
It's...

854
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,590
It's about the rebirth
of Empress Wu Zetian.

855
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:12,270
Rebirth?

856
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:18,370
